{"tid":2022286,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"夏蘭特的成功秘訣：身體前傾？","createTime":"2020-05-18T08:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T10:15:41.000Z","uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"caa20bbd1ac883ffe3bcc007bb3e19fa045d1c3b","tid":2022286,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/sportsyeah.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/B314341C-3115-4B4E-A8FE-9DE2CD09C1EB-scaled.jpeg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fsportsyeah.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2FB314341C-3115-4B4E-A8FE-9DE2CD09C1EB-scaled.jpeg%3Fresize%3D1536%252C864%26ssl%3D1&h=25eb716f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係夏蘭特（Erling Haaland）！這位在今年一月加盟多蒙特的挪威神鋒登陸德甲，頭9場貢獻了10個入球，並協助多蒙特在德甲復賽首戰4-0擊敗死敵史浩克04。夏蘭特衝刺力驚人，令多支球隊的後衛招架不來。如果各位球迷仔細留意，不難發現夏蘭特的起跑動作異於一般球員：他的身體總是稍向前傾。<br />\n<br />\n夏蘭特身高1.94米、體重90公斤，從以上的數據看來他應該一位標準的中鋒。但是，夏蘭特的賣點卻不是其身型，而是他的驚人衝刺力。他擅長捕捉兩名敵衛之間的空檔、切入對手防線的身後，把握入球機會。在多蒙特的進攻體系，不乏能送出致命直線的好手，夏蘭特予取予攜、入球如拾草芥。但是，夏蘭特如此高大，為何能如此輕巧？<br />\n<br />\n關鍵在於他起步的時候，總愛把身體向前傾&mdash;&mdash;觀乎100公尺短跑世界紀錄保持者保特（Usain Bolt），亦是以這種動作換來優勢。<br />\n<br />\n根據學者研究，身體向前傾有助對抗空氣阻力，而且骨盆重心置於正中間，使運動員跑步時集中力量至臀部肌肉。不過，這種跑姿只適用於短跑，而且當跑到30公尺之後，便不再有加速的優勢。但是，這種跑姿對於一個需要短途爆發的前鋒球員來說已經夠用了。<br />\n<br />\n但掌握這種跑姿並不容易。隨著身體前傾，落地的衝擊會加劇，如果步頻（走路或者跑步時，每分鐘腳步落地的次數）未經訓練，你的腳步會跟不上前傾、然後失衡，而且這對球員的身體控制有嚴格要求。如果夏蘭特沒有經過田徑選手的訓練，不可能如此駕輕就熟。<br />\n<br />\n參考文章：<br />\nDoes Leaning Forward Help You Run More Efficiently by Letting Gravity Do Some of the Work?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.runnersworld.com/training/a20814323/does-leaning-forward-help-you-run-more-efficiently-by-letting-gravity-do-some-of-the-work/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.runnersworld.com%2Ftraining%2Fa20814323%2Fdoes-leaning-forward-help-you-run-more-efficiently-by-letting-gravity-do-some-of-the-work%2F&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCh4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=ffd036db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.runnersworld.com/training/a20814323/does-leaning-forward-help-you-run-more-efficiently-by-letting-gravity-do-some-of-the-work/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sportsyeah.hk/2020/05/sportsreport/sportsyeah/32252/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsportsyeah.hk%2F2020%2F05%2Fsportsreport%2Fsportsyeah%2F32252%2F&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCh4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=0745f45d\" target=\"_blank\">https://sportsyeah.hk/2020/05/sportsreport/sportsyeah/32252/</a>"},{"pid":"5fcd3291c2903afd13f4c285350fc26a81e6148e","tid":2022286,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:52:16.000Z","msg":"吹大左"},{"pid":"f523fcc6415c0bcf0c3de3a6670fb03a0a1d81c8","tid":2022286,"uid":46911,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p5bMny0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp5bMny0.jpg&h=6ad1edee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00e9150662b290b9f67579a368fd732840227e31","tid":2022286,"uid":47268,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5fcd3291c2903afd13f4c285350fc26a81e6148e","tid":2022286,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:52:16.000Z","msg":"吹大左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"我懷疑你場場都買夏蘭特首名入球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68c168da88ae8b6e66c2bd140a04631077bbbd6","tid":2022286,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00e9150662b290b9f67579a368fd732840227e31","tid":2022286,"uid":47268,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5fcd3291c2903afd13f4c285350fc26a81e6148e","tid":2022286,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:52:16.000Z","msg":"吹大左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"我懷疑你場場都買夏蘭特首名入球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:11:59.000Z